name.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Don't Judge a Video by its Thumbnail

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Youtubers have their ways of attracting you to view their videos, sometimes it's the thumbnail, other times the titles are what sparks our curiosity to click in. Youtube is a platform to post videos, so what happens if we were to remove the videos? Would you still be on there just to listen to the audio?
